{"tid":1479602,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"烈女好怕死 別提六四 mv","createTime":"2019-08-17T03:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T04:11:18.000Z","uid":290652,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc749760914c8969b671dfe72be5b28aa11c3e3e","tid":1479602,"uid":290652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"《烈女》<br />\n<br />\n改詞：雲<br />\n唱： 水<br />\n<br />\n香港觀眾話佢賤人話佢變節變心<br />\n緊守黨委派的指引 楊女士便行運<br />\n暪住利君亞 深圳過關到處獻媚<br />\n讓盲目擁戴者心死<br />\n倒轉是與非 與 fish man 在一起<br />\n<br />\n烈女好怕死 別提六四<br />\n極害怕失去北上嘅商機<br />\n英勇表態愛護五星旗<br />\n是為了當上中國嘅歌姬<br />\n<br />\n烈女好怕死 絕無傲氣<br />\n早已失去性格和品味<br />\n春晚演唱吃夠了負皮<br />\n期待你日後名譽掃地 呸呸<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hmsy1nkrP1A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhmsy1nkrP1A&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75W9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=96c1529f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hmsy1nkrP1A</a>"},{"pid":"ab6cd13843e947a6677c78d953b5f3b20a157cf8","tid":1479602,"uid":31609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0a05892eda1c8d5d626d42ca52fda6a522cbd2","tid":1479602,"uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:44:37.000Z","msg":"大家一定要全面杯葛依啲人<br />\n<br />\n佢唔幫香港人講野唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n因為咁只係代表佢唔需要再賺香港人嘅錢<br />\n<br />\n我地作為香港人一蚊都唔好比佢賺<br />\n<br />\n將啲錢比返真正愛香港嘅歌手藝人<br />\n<br />\n例如徐天佑 關淑儀"},{"pid":"8299b77a9bdb7e2ceccea668a710ef82e6273431","tid":1479602,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"佢好似以前未做偽人之前<br />\n<br />\n做過護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}